Theses are NS4 install scripts to help you download, install, run NS4 quickly.We have tested it successfully on Ubuntu 16.04.

We recommend to install NS4 step by step, because there may be some errors in the installation process.We also provide a one-click installation script(install_deps.sh) to install NS4. 
 
At first, You need to add a new user named kphf1995cm because ns4 programs rely on some file path, of course this is optional, if not you need to modify NS4 code.

create new user:
$cd /home/kphf1995cm
$sudo su

Then you can choose one of the following ways to install NS4.
install NS4 step by step:
1 install ns3 
bash install_ns3_pre.sh
bash install_ns3.sh
2 install bmv2
bash install_bmv2.sh
3 install p4c-bm
bash install_p4c-bm.sh
4 install ns4
bash install_ns4.sh
bash create_ns4_run.sh

install NS4 one step:
bash install_deps.sh

If everything goes well, then come to this folder(/home/kphf1995cm/ns-allinone-3.27/ns-3.27) and run ns4.
$ cd /home/kphf1995cm/ns-allinone-3.27/ns-3.27
$ bash run.sh
If it runs successfully, you can look up the result in this file(res.txt)
$ cat res.txt

